Articles.Content:
I was watching this video

when i noticed he was using slow motion and i figured he was using a mod. So i looked on the forums for a "dynamic warp mod" because the thing that popped up said "dynamic warp 1/4" or "1/8". Do any of you have an idea of what that mod was.

This was a mod called Dynamic Warp, it was made by the infamous DEADBEEF, who has also made other incredible mods such as Editor Tools and Subassembly saver/loader. Sadly, he disappeared a few months ago, and all of his mods no longer work.

Spica
I haven't seen anything for .21 but dynamic warp was working for .20. See this : http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/showthread.php/27524-Where-is-the-Dynamic-warp-mod?p=440628&viewfull=1#post440628
